text.tspan: a.k.a. The Nine Points of Roguery
A-part ~ D/G D D/Bm C/Em | D/G D D A/D
B-part ~ C/G D D/Bm C/Em | C/G D D A/D
Source: Maggie Sansone (Mist and Stone, 1990) plus bits of https://thesession.org/tunes/429
Notes: It seems many versions of this tune place an Em chord in the fourth bar of both parts.
Maggie goes to a C instead, and I like that.
